2. Write an SQL query to retrieve count of items and total price of each order.
---------------------------------------------------------------
SELECT
    oi.order_id,
    COUNT(oi.item_id) AS NumberOfItems,
    SUM(i.unit_price * oi.quantity) AS TotalPrice
FROM
    item i,
    order_item oi
WHERE
    i.item_id = oi.item_id
GROUP BY
    order_id
